eas_text: A civil authority has issued A REQUIRED MONTHLY TEST for the following counties or areas: Pacific; Grays Harbor, WA; at 03:49 PM ON JAN 7, 2026 Effective until 07:49 PM. Message from WSLF/CAP.
extra_text: This is the Pacific County Emergency Management Agency with a scheduled test of the Emergency Alert System. If this were an actual Emergency you would be instructed where to tune for official instructions and information.
